<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>HEATED BLADES</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Fafard">Fafard</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 9:19 a.m. 29/6/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> HEATED BLADES<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Hello, I am Fafard Dragonfire from the Xegony server and I have come to ye to tell you of a great battle to take place for prizes and fame!

<P>It a battle to the death, a game? Some say so, but to others it is honor.
<BR>Come play in a game were the dueling is fair as can be, and prizes are givin.
<BR>You think your charatcer is a buffed fighter?? Wait untill you fight in this heated battle.
<P>The next dueling match Heated Blades will have is Sunday, the 11th in July.
<BR>We will meet in Kithicor woods near the zone line of East Commonlands.
<BR>The time to sign up will be at 8AM upto 9:45AM. The start of dueling is at 10AM EST timezone.
<BR>I hope all that wish to come can, I can be E-Mailed (gamewhiz@home.com) if people would like a time/date change or more information.
<P>For more information goto http://www.eqhouse.com/hb.htm.
<P>Due to lack of prizes (donations are very welcomed), the level range of this one match (the upccoming matching will have a higher range) is set at level 1 upto 24 may join.
<P>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
<P ALIGN=CENTER><EM><A HREF="http://www.eqhouse.com" TARGET=_top>House of EverQuest</A></EM></P>
